'''Abregada-rae Spaceport''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] and largest [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] of [[Abregado-rae/Legends|Abregado-rae]]. It contained many [[Water/Legends|water]] canals which were used for transportation. The older part of the [[City/Legends|city]] was referred to as the [[Old Patch]]. The city had numerous sights, such as the [[LoBue Cantina]].

